title: This Month's GTA+ Benefits
headline: This Month's GTA+ Benefits
subtitle: GTA+
content:
In addition to the recurring monthly GTA$500,000 deposited directly into your Maze Bank account, GTA+ members who've signed up for this month (February 8 - March 6) will also receive:

— The Ocelot Jugular
— Access to the Vinewood Club Garage
— Exclusive clothing
— 2X GTA$ and RP on Casino Work and Story Missions
— 40% off the Casino Penthouse
— And more

Membership automatically renews monthly, cancel any time. Visit rsg.ms/gtaplus for more info.
